  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Apollo Hospitals Enterprise Limited (Apollo or the company) is the holding company of the largest private integrated healthcare group in India, with 16 owned and 24 managed hospitals (bed capacity of over 5,000), a network of 206 retail pharmacies and a healthcare management consulting practice.  Through a number of joint ventures and associated companies, its business lines include also clinical and diagnostic services, medical business process outsourcing and insurance services.

Apollo is in the process of raising funds for the implementation of the companys strategy, designed to strengthen its position of a market leader by taking advantage of existing growth and consolidation opportunities in its domestic market, as well as build on its established brand name by expanding to new markets.</narrative>
  </description>
